---
// Hero-adjacent pull-quote: featured Pam Connealy testimonial, placed right below the Overture
// so social proof is the first thing after the headline.
---

<section class="bg-paper-soft border-y border-rule py-14 md:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 md:gap-12 items-start" data-reveal>
      <!-- Attribution rail -->
      <div class="md:col-span-3">
        <p class="small-caps text-copper mb-3">Recommendation</p>
        <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-ink-muted mb-4">Live on LinkedIn</p>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-copper pl-4">
          <p class="font-display text-xl text-ink leading-tight">Pam Connealy</p>
          <p class="text-ink-muted text-sm mt-1 leading-snug">Former CFO and COO, Immunovant</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Quote -->
      <blockquote class="md:col-span-9 relative">
        <span class="absolute -left-4 md:-left-8 -top-6 md:-top-10 font-display text-7xl md:text-9xl text-copper/30 leading-none select-none">"</span>
        <p class="font-display-italic text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-[1.75rem] text-ink leading-[1.35] relative">
          She didn't just move documents around. She understood what was in them, flagged issues before they became problems, and brought structured problem-solving to high-level executive operations. Any executive team would be lucky to have her.
        </p>
        <footer class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-baseline gap-x-4 gap-y-1 text-sm">
          <span class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-muted">Verified outcomes:</span>
          <span class="text-ink">25% reporting accuracy lift</span>
          <span class="text-ink-muted">&middot;</span>
          <span class="text-ink">22% satisfaction lift</span>
          <span class="text-ink-muted">&middot;</span>
          <span class="text-ink">20% faster EA onboarding</span>
        </footer>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
